🛠️ Tools Used

🐍 Programming Language

Python – for data analysis, modeling, and scripting

📦 Python Libraries

Pandas – for data manipulation and analysis

NumPy – for numerical computations

Scikit-learn – for machine learning models and evaluation

Imbalanced-learn (imblearn) – for SMOTE and handling class imbalance

Matplotlib / Seaborn – for data visualization

XGBoost – for high-performance gradient boosting classifier

🧪 Development Environment

Jupyter Notebook – for interactive code development and experimentation



🗃️ Dataset Source

Kaggle – Credit Card Fraud Detection dataset:
https://www.kaggle.com/mlg-ulb/creditcardfraud
